<br>
So far, i've seen concerns from long time members in our guild that in any switchover to dkp, that those who have been around a long time, or perhaps contributed a lot of time or effort so far, well, that gets lost if everyone starts out with zero points.<br>
<br>
I guess it just doesn't seem too easy to switch a guild over to dkp, without some members feeling slighted.<br>
<br>
